EPP Task is an easy preprocessor ant task.

The next directives are supported:
#ifdef 
#ifndef
#else
#endif
#include

Put epptask.jar to ant's lib directory to use the task.
See epp.html for the complete documentation.

Simple example:
<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<project basedir="." default="test">
  <taskdef resource="epp.task" />
  <target name="test">
    <epp srcfile="in" destfile="out" defs="DEBUG, UNIX" />
  </target>
</project>
